h2. Problem

Database not created by [Titanium.Database.install()|http://developer.appcelerator.com/apidoc/mobile/latest/Titanium.Database.install-method.html] if file does not exist.

It's expected to create an empty sqlite file if no file exists.

Note: works as expected on Android


h2. Test case

{code:lang=javascript}
var db = Ti.Database.install('mydb1', 'mydb1Installed');
{code}

h2. Logs

{code}
